  "description": "<p><strong>谷歌收购摩托罗拉移动部门后最重要的一个产品Moto X又有新消息传来，加拿大运营商Rogers内部透露的消息，这款机型预计将在今年八月份左右发布，届时将有黑白两个版本一同销售。</strong>有趣的是基于Google的语音命令系统将首次出现在Android智能机上。除此之外，Moto X还有新的玩法，例如只需要抖手腕两次就可以启动拍照应用，而点击屏幕任何地方就可以当成快门按钮等等。<br /></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2ea3ca16/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244622.htm&amp;t=Moto+X+%E9%A2%84%E8%AE%A1%E5%B0%86%E5%9C%A8%E5%85%AB%E6%9C%88%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83+%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E8%AF%AD%E9%9F%B3%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244622.htm&amp;t=Moto+X+%E9%A2%84%E8%AE%A1%E5%B0%86%E5%9C%A8%E5%85%AB%E6%9C%88%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83+%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E8%AF%AD%E9%9F%B3%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244622.htm&amp;t=Moto+X+%E9%A2%84%E8%AE%A1%E5%B0%86%E5%9C%A8%E5%85%AB%E6%9C%88%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83+%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E8%AF%AD%E9%9F%B3%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244622.htm&amp;t=Moto+X+%E9%A2%84%E8%AE%A1%E5%B0%86%E5%9C%A8%E5%85%AB%E6%9C%88%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83+%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E8%AF%AD%E9%9F%B3%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244622.htm&amp;t=Moto+X+%E9%A2%84%E8%AE%A1%E5%B0%86%E5%9C%A8%E5%